'''Lorcia Cooper-Khumalo''' (yavutse 9 Ugushyingo 1978), ni umukinnyi wa  filime n'umubyinnyi muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]  . <ref name="tvsa">https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=4384</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri serivise zizwi cyane za televiziyo ''Lockdown'', ''Zulu Wedding'' and ''Hey Boy'' <ref>http://www.702.co.za/articles/239838/actress-lorcia-cooper-swaps-dance-moves-for-prison-life</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 9 Ugushyingo 1978 i Cape Town, muri Afurika y'Epfo. Yashakanye na Mandla Khumalo. <ref>https://www.dailyvoice.co.za/lifestyle-entertainment/celebrity/call-me-mrs-khumalo-19693366</ref> Abashakanye bafite umukobwa umwe n'umuhungu umwe. <ref name="briefly">https://briefly.co.za/33358-lorcia-cooper-biography-age-eyes-married-family-khumalo-lockdown-backstage-instagram.html</ref>

Muri 2019, yarwaye lymph node yabyimbye muri tiroyide. Kugira ngo avurwe, yatewe inshinge za karuboni ya dioxyde de puffness mu jisho. <ref>https://www.timeslive.co.za/tshisa-live/tshisa-live/2019-11-01-watch--lorcia-cooper-opens-up-about-her-struggles-with-her-thyroid/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Igihe yari afite imyaka ine, ababyeyi be bamwandikishije mu ishuri ryo kubyina nyuma yo kubona ko akunda kubyina kandi yitabira amarushanwa yo kubyina yo muri Amerika y'Epfo na Ballroom. Afite imyaka itanu, yatsindiye amarushanwa ye ya mbere muri shampiyona yintara kubyina Ballroom ndetse nimbyino zo muri Amerika y'Epfo. Afite imyaka umunani, yize mu ishuri ry’imbyino kandi yiga kubyina iyobowe n’umukorikori uzwi cyane witwa Debby Turner, wabaye umujyanama n’umuyobozi. Nyuma yaje kwinjira mu ishuri ry’imbyino rya North West Arts Council aho yagize amahirwe yo kuba umwarimu mu myaka yashize. Igihe yari afite imyaka 19, yatsindiye igihembo cyiza cya FNB Vita.  <ref>https://www.osmtalent.com/artist/lorcia-cooper-kumalo/</ref>

Nyuma yaje kwifatanya numuyoboro wa SABC2 ahinduka Travel Xplorer. Muri kiriya gihe, yatumiriwe gukina 'Cindi' muri filime ''Hey Boy'' iyobowe na Andre Odendaal yerekanwe mu 2003. Muri 2008, yagizwe umwe mu bacamanza mu marushanwa yo kubyina, ''Dans!'' ''Dans!'' ''Dans!'' byerekanwe kuri ykNET. Mu mwaka wa 2008, yabaye umucuranzi wa koreografi n'umucamanza mu marushanwa nyayo, 'High School Musical: Spotlight Africa yepfo' yanyuze kuri M-Net.  

Muri 2017, yakinnye muri Mzansi Magic show, ''Lockdown'' afite uruhare rwa 'Tyson' muri saison yayo ya kane. <ref>https://www.edgars.co.za/why-lockdown-s-lorcia-cooper-doesn-t-need-hollywood</ref> Muri uwo mwaka, yakinnye 'Marang' muri firime ya ''Zulu'' .  Muri Werurwe 2019, yatsindiye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza kurusha abandi muri SAFTA ibihembo kubera uruhare rwe muri ''Lockdown 2'' .  Muri Nzeri 2020, yagaragaye mu ikinamico ya Mzansi ''Abakozi bo mu rugo'' afite uruhare 'Mkhonto'. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/news/lorcia-cooper-on-playing-mkhonto-and-the-lack-of-leading-roles-for-coloured-actors-20200904</ref>

